<h1 data-section-id="klap8k" data-start="591" data-end="612">Task 3 Project Idea</h1>
<p data-start="613" data-end="677">Create a <strong data-start="622" data-end="677">Responsive Landing Page using HTML, CSS, JavaScript</strong></p>
<p data-start="679" data-end="739">Example:<br data-start="687" data-end="690">
<strong data-start="690" data-end="739">Dental Clinic Landing Page (Improved Version)</strong></p>
