mages</code> folder</strong> is used to store all the pictures used in your website.</p>
<p data-start="81" data-end="169">In your <strong data-start="89" data-end="107">Task 3 project</strong>, the images folder contains the pictures for dental services.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1w7tdm6" data-start="171" data-end="200">Example Project Structure</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="201" data-end="346"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>task3/</span><br><span>│</span><br><span>├── index.html</span><br><span>├── style.css</span><br><span>├── script.js</span><br><span>├── images/</span><br><span>│   ├── cleaning.jpg</span><br><span>│   ├── braces.jpg</span><br><span>│   └── implant.jpg</span><br><span>└── README.md</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-section-id="1k4tbl6" data-start="348" data-end="382">Why we use the <code data-start="367" data-end="375">images</code> folder</h3>
<p data-start="383" data-end="471">✅ Keeps project organized<br data-start="408" data-end="411">
✅ All pictures stored in one place<br data-start="445" data-end="448">
✅ Easy to manage images</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1pn8qzt" data-start="473" data-end="504">How images are used in HTML</h3>
<p data-start="506" data-end="531">Example in <strong data-start="517" data-end="531">index.html</strong></p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="533" data-end="597"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>HTML</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost size-9" aria-label="Edit"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-mx-1 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></div></button></span><div aria-label="Toggle view" class="group relative flex gap-0.5 rounded-full p-0.5 bg-token-bg-secondary dark:bg-gray-1000"><div aria-hidden="true" class="bg-token-bg-primary pointer-events-none absolute start-0.5 top-0.5 h-8 w-8 rounded-full" style="transform: none;"></div><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="Code" aria-pressed="true" class="relative flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center transition-colors text-token-text-primary group-hover:text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#00f12a" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="Preview" aria-pressed="false" aria-disabled="false" class="relative flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center transition-colors text-token-text-secondary group-hover:text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼg">&lt;img</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">src</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"images/cleaning.jpg"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">alt</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"Teeth Cleaning"</span><span class="ͼg">&gt;</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div><div class="flex w-full justify-end px-3 mt-1" data-code-block-feedback-row="true"></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="599" data-end="610">This means:</p>
<ul data-start="611" data-end="672">
<li data-section-id="1mz44ex" data-start="611" data-end="636">
<p data-start="613" data-end="636">Go to <strong data-start="619" data-end="636">images folder</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1i32tn1" data-start="637" data-end="672">
<p data-start="639" data-end="672">Load the picture <strong data-start="656" data-end="672">cleaning.jpg</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="wzk0gi" data-start="674" data-end="702">If you don't have images</h3>
<p data-start="703" data-end="728">You have <strong data-start="712" data-end="727">two options</strong>:</p>
<p data-start="730" data-end="791"><strong data-start="730" data-end="750">Option 1 (Easy):</strong><br data-start="750" data-end="753">
Remove the <code data-start="764" data-end="771">&lt;img&gt;</code> tags from the HTML.</p>
<p data-start="793" data-end="903"><strong data-start="793" data-end="830">Option 2 (Better for internship):</strong><br>
Download some dental images and place them inside the <strong data-start="885" data-end="902">images folder</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="905" data-end="920">Example images:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="921" data-end="992"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>cleaning.jpg</span><br><span>braces.jpg</span><br><span>implant.jpg</span><br><span>whitening.jpg</span><br><span>rootcanal.jpg</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="994" data-end="1021">Then upload them to GitHub.</p>
<hr data-start="1023" data-end="1026">
<p data-start="1028" data-end="1164" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">If you want, I can also give you <strong data-start="1061" data-end="1160">10 high-quality dental clinic images that will load fast and look professional in your project.</strong> 🦷✨</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><but