 images are OK</strong>, but it is better if they are <strong data-start="59" data-end="86">related to your project</strong> (dental clinic services) so your <strong data-start="120" data-end="149">Task 3 looks professional</strong> for the internship.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="11a68kp" data-start="171" data-end="193">Good images to use</h3>
<p data-start="194" data-end="243">Put images like these in the <strong data-start="223" data-end="242"><code data-start="225" data-end="233">images</code> folder</strong>:</p>
