<h3 data-section-id="jdw2xb" data-start="624" data-end="640">Important ⚠️</h3>
<p data-start="641" data-end="700">The <strong data-start="645" data-end="700">image name in HTML must match the file name exactly</strong></p>
<p data-start="702" data-end="727">Example in <strong data-start="713" data-end="727">index.html</strong></p>
